                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18031026-44-defend280 t18031026-44-punish250"></join>
               fined 6s. 8d
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron Thompson.</p>
